<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_223752d9-129e-45a1-bc70-047e926a0449" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><sptc>C4D14</sptc><title id="_0b8c01b7-5852-4178-aae1-26eccee2272e">Venting of grease traps</title><archive-num>2019: H202.4g</archive-num><subclause id="_25e5299e-fddc-4020-bfc7-c10bccbe7348" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9a38f493-6003-49dc-a1ff-8df049f2a68c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Grease trap chambers must provide adequate ventilation by providing—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_32b8e90c-7cae-41e2-89d2-c3ef05abd031">two DN 100 vents in addition to the ventilation provided for the sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1249_0.8.0.xml#_25307451-c7e1-4167-b4de-e5a1af26694c" id="_ed93d6fd-ef64-4574-8106-57c945fd4e7a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage</xref> system; or</li><li id="_37f3c39d-4899-4026-be70-b05dc4cd0337">appropriate mechanical ventilation.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_4e5b1e39-1648-4999-8070-9818c19cbd06" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d0ebd019-93d6-4c21-83dd-09f940e4799f">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Anti-siphon vents must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_9a92a114-9af9-4eb8-a26b-e9c875498ffd">a minimum of DN 50: and</li><li id="_83a6d54c-2cdf-4330-b2b5-8b738a1c00be">connected to the outlet of the grease trap chamber.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_0b0dd046-57d5-4d83-ae12-b05a0b657e04"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>See <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7754_0.3.0.xml#_6e766e76-39cf-4c36-92a3-92ee63dfa85e" id="_9640ae31-037e-4d2b-b36f-22517751040f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">TAS Figure C4D14a</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7755_0.3.0.xml#_9ec7cf61-9d45-4293-ae8f-116a28fabca9" id="_d180e68d-27c5-4b30-a2a4-38a6258ce209" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">TAS Figure C4D14b</xref> for typical venting arrangement for grease trap chambers.</p><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7754_0.3.0.xml" id="_6e766e76-39cf-4c36-92a3-92ee63dfa85e" variation="TAS"><num/><title id="_df88a5f1-8231-45da-bdb5-0a9ac6a9d042"/></image-reference><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7755_0.3.0.xml" id="_9ec7cf61-9d45-4293-ae8f-116a28fabca9" variation="TAS"><num/><title id="_d1194f15-1725-45cf-8425-6dfaf1a0a0a6"/></image-reference></callout></clause>